## ── PART 8: Data Cleaning Checklist ────────────────
##
## Before training, ALWAYS:
##
##   □ Check for missing values
##   □ Remove duplicates
##   □ Normalize numerical features
##   □ Encode categorical features
##   □ Check for outliers
##   □ Split into train/test sets
##
## ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

print("PART 8: Data Cleaning Checklist")
print("─────────────────────────────────")
print("")

print("Before training, ALWAYS:")
print("  □ Check for missing values")
print("  □ Remove duplicates")
print("  □ Normalize numerical features")
print("  □ Encode categorical features")
print("  □ Check for outliers")
print("  □ Split into train/test sets")
print("")

